body:
Hey, It's me, WildCards and I put together a Scrimmage server file for you guys until the nise update. It comes with justice 2 and I Will be updating it in the future.

Current Maps:
  • Justice 2 - UmbreonMessiah
  • Arizona - UmbreonMessiah
  • Justice 3 - UmbreonMessiah
  • Alpha Complex - UmbreonMessiah

The download is here: http://www.mediafire.com/download/b8osxi2k4ar4ro2/Scrim+Server.zip

Map Requirements
  • Must be accepted
  • Must have a valid YML/YAML
  • Must have a download and permission from the creator
Map Request:
Name of map:
IGN of creator:
Skype of creator (If you are the creator, then you just need to say you have permission):
Download:


NOTE: I did not make these map or the plugin. I only made the xml and put it together.
Also mods, lock this if it is against the rules.
